# Binance Market Data Pipeline — Full-Depth TimescaleDB Ingestion

Build a production-grade Binance data ingestion system for **Spot + USDT-margined Futures**, storing into the **existing TimescaleDB** instance (same as BingX). Curated pair set, same Tailscale egress. Targets Nautilus Trader backtesting with maximum data depth.

## Pairs (curated, same as BingX)

| Pair | Spot | Futures |
|---|---|---|
| ALGOUSDT | ✅ | ✅ |
| BNBUSDT | ✅ | ✅ |
| BTCUSDT | ✅ | ✅ |
| ETHUSDT | ✅ | ✅ |
| PAXGUSDT | ✅ | ✅ |
| SOLUSDT | ✅ | ✅ |
| XRPUSDT | ✅ | ✅ |

---

## Complete Data Sources for Nautilus Trader

### Spot + Futures (shared)

| Data Type | REST Endpoint | WS Stream | Backfill Depth | DB Table |
|---|---|---|---|---|
| **Kline/Candles** | `/api/v3/klines` · `/fapi/v1/klines` | `@kline_<interval>` | Full history | `binance_candles` |
| **Agg Trades** | `/api/v3/aggTrades` · `/fapi/v1/aggTrades` | `@aggTrade` | Full history | `binance_agg_trades` |
| **Order Book** | `/api/v3/depth` · `/fapi/v1/depth` | `@depth@100ms` | Live only | `binance_orderbook_snapshots` |
| **24h Ticker** | `/api/v3/ticker/24hr` · `/fapi/v1/ticker/24hr` | `@ticker` | Live only | `binance_tickers` |
| **Exchange Info** | `/api/v3/exchangeInfo` · `/fapi/v1/exchangeInfo` | — | Snapshot | `binance_exchange_info` |

### Futures-exclusive data

| Data Type | REST Endpoint | WS Stream | Backfill Depth | DB Table |
|---|---|---|---|---|
| **Funding Rate** | `/fapi/v1/fundingRate` | via `@markPrice` | Full history (limit 1000/req) | `binance_funding_rates` |
| **Open Interest** | `/fapi/v1/openInterest` | — | Current only | `binance_open_interest` |
| **OI Statistics** | `/futures/data/openInterestHist` | — | 30 days | `binance_oi_statistics` |
| **Mark Price Klines** | `/fapi/v1/markPriceKlines` | `@markPrice@1s` | Full history | `binance_mark_price_klines` |
| **Index Price Klines** | `/fapi/v1/indexPriceKlines` | — | Full history | `binance_index_price_klines` |
| **Premium Index Klines** | `/fapi/v1/premiumIndexKlines` | — | Full history | `binance_premium_index_klines` |
| **Top Trader L/S (Positions)** | `/futures/data/topLongShortPositionRatio` | — | 30 days | `binance_top_ls_position_ratio` |
| **Top Trader L/S (Accounts)** | `/futures/data/topLongShortAccountRatio` | — | 30 days | `binance_top_ls_account_ratio` |
| **Global L/S Ratio** | `/futures/data/globalLongShortAccountRatio` | — | 30 days | `binance_global_ls_ratio` |
| **Taker Buy/Sell Volume** | `/futures/data/takerlongshortRatio` | — | 30 days | `binance_taker_buy_sell_volume` |
| **Basis** | `/futures/data/basis` | — | 30 days | `binance_basis` |

> [!NOTE]
> Sentiment endpoints (OI stats, L/S ratios, taker volume, basis) only retain 30 days of history on Binance. We'll backfill the full 30 days immediately and then poll continuously to accumulate depth. The `period` parameter supports: `5m`, `15m`, `30m`, `1h`, `2h`, `4h`, `6h`, `12h`, `1d`.

