## Proposed Changes

### 1. Config & Catalog

#### [MODIFY] [env.ts](file:///Users/itsnk/Desktop/Coding/tv-goldviewfx/backend/src/config/env.ts)

Add Binance env vars:
```
BINANCE_API_KEY, BINANCE_SECRET_KEY
BINANCE_SPOT_BASE_URL (default https://api.binance.com)
BINANCE_FUTURES_BASE_URL (default https://fapi.binance.com)
BINANCE_SPOT_WS_URL (default wss://stream.binance.com:9443)
BINANCE_FUTURES_WS_URL (default wss://fstream.binance.com)
BINANCE_MARKET_DATA_ENABLED, BINANCE_WS_ENABLED, BINANCE_BACKFILL_ENABLED
BINANCE_MARKET_DATA_PAIRS (CSV, default "ALGOUSDT,BNBUSDT,BTCUSDT,ETHUSDT,PAXGUSDT,SOLUSDT,XRPUSDT")
BINANCE_INGEST_INTERVALS (default "1m,3m,5m,15m,30m,1h,2h,4h,6h,8h,12h,1d,3d,1w,1M")
BINANCE_BACKFILL_MAX_BATCHES (default 50000)
BINANCE_WS_FLUSH_INTERVAL_MS (default 1000)
BINANCE_WS_RECONNECT_MIN_MS (default 1000)
```

