---

### 2. Database Layer

#### [NEW] [binance_market_data.ts](file:///Users/itsnk/Desktop/Coding/tv-goldviewfx/backend/src/db/timescale/binance_market_data.ts)

Uses existing `TIMESCALE_URL` connection. Schema creation in `ensureBinanceMarketDataSchema()`:

**13 hypertables:**

```sql
-- Core market data (spot + futures)
binance_candles (exchange, pair, interval, open_time PK, close_time, open, high, low, close,
  volume, quote_volume, trade_count, taker_buy_base_vol, taker_buy_quote_vol, source)

binance_agg_trades (exchange, pair, agg_trade_id PK, price, quantity, first_trade_id,
  last_trade_id, executed_at, is_buyer_maker, source)

binance_orderbook_snapshots (exchange, pair, captured_at PK, depth_level, bids JSONB, asks JSONB, source)

binance_tickers (exchange, pair, captured_at PK, last_price, price_change, price_change_pct,
  weighted_avg_price, open_price, high_price, low_price, volume, quote_volume,
  open_time, close_time, trade_count, source)

binance_exchange_info (exchange, symbol PK, status, base_asset, quote_asset, filters JSONB,
  maker_fee, taker_fee, captured_at)

-- Futures-exclusive
binance_funding_rates (pair, funding_time PK, funding_rate, mark_price, source)

binance_open_interest (pair, captured_at PK, open_interest, source)

binance_oi_statistics (pair, period, captured_at PK, sum_oi, sum_oi_value, source)

binance_mark_price_klines (pair, interval, open_time PK, open, high, low, close, source)

binance_index_price_klines (pair, interval, open_time PK, open, high, low, close, source)

binance_premium_index_klines (pair, interval, open_time PK, open, high, low, close, source)

-- Sentiment data (futures, 30-day rolling window)
binance_ls_ratio (pair, ratio_type, period, captured_at PK, long_short_ratio,
  long_account, short_account, source)
  -- ratio_type: 'top_position' | 'top_account' | 'global'

binance_taker_buy_sell (pair, period, captured_at PK, buy_sell_ratio, buy_vol, sell_vol, source)

binance_basis (pair, period, captured_at PK, index_price, futures_price, basis, basis_rate,
  annualized_basis_rate, contract_type, source)
```

#### [NEW] [backend/src/db/repositories/binance_market_data/](file:///Users/itsnk/Desktop/Coding/tv-goldviewfx/backend/src/db/repositories/binance_market_data/)

Repository files: [candles.ts](file:///Users/itsnk/Desktop/Coding/tv-goldviewfx/convex/bingx_candles.ts), `agg_trades.ts`, [orderbook_snapshots.ts](file:///Users/itsnk/Desktop/Coding/tv-goldviewfx/convex/bingx_orderbook_snapshots.ts), [tickers.ts](file:///Users/itsnk/Desktop/Coding/tv-goldviewfx/convex/bingx_tickers.ts), `exchange_info.ts`, [funding_rates.ts](file:///Users/itsnk/Desktop/Coding/tv-goldviewfx/convex/bingx_funding_rates.ts), [open_interest.ts](file:///Users/itsnk/Desktop/Coding/tv-goldviewfx/convex/bingx_open_interest.ts), `oi_statistics.ts`, `mark_price_klines.ts`, `index_price_klines.ts`, `premium_index_klines.ts`, `ls_ratio.ts`, `taker_buy_sell.ts`, `basis.ts`, [index.ts](file:///Users/itsnk/Desktop/Coding/tv-goldviewfx/index.ts).

