### 3. Core Services

#### [NEW] [binance_client.ts](file:///Users/itsnk/Desktop/Coding/tv-goldviewfx/backend/src/integrations/exchange/binance_client.ts)

REST client with:
- HMAC-SHA256 signing (for authenticated endpoints)
- Rate limit tracking from `X-MBX-USED-WEIGHT-1M` headers
- Adaptive throttle: sleeps when weight budget >80% consumed
- Retry + exponential backoff on 429/418
- Separate base URLs for spot vs futures
- All REST methods listed in the data source tables above

#### [NEW] [binance_spot_ingest.ts](file:///Users/itsnk/Desktop/Coding/tv-goldviewfx/backend/src/services/binance_spot_ingest.ts)

For each pair: candles (all intervals), agg trades, orderbook snapshot, 24h ticker. Uses DB-latest tracking for incremental fetches.

#### [NEW] [binance_futures_ingest.ts](file:///Users/itsnk/Desktop/Coding/tv-goldviewfx/backend/src/services/binance_futures_ingest.ts)

All spot data types plus: funding rates, OI, OI stats, mark/index/premium price klines, L/S ratios (3 types), taker buy/sell, basis. Each sentiment endpoint uses `period` parameter for granularity.

#### [NEW] [binance_market_data_ws.ts](file:///Users/itsnk/Desktop/Coding/tv-goldviewfx/backend/src/services/binance_market_data_ws.ts)

**Spot streams** (`wss://stream.binance.com:9443/stream?streams=...`):
- `<symbol>@kline_<interval>`, `<symbol>@aggTrade`, `<symbol>@depth@100ms`, `<symbol>@ticker`

**Futures streams** (`wss://fstream.binance.com/stream?streams=...`):
- `<symbol>@kline_<interval>`, `<symbol>@aggTrade`, `<symbol>@depth@100ms`, `<symbol>@ticker`, `<symbol>@markPrice@1s`

Architecture: buffered flush, auto-reconnect, ping/pong keepalive, sequence anomaly detection.

#### [NEW] [binance_full_backfill_service.ts](file:///Users/itsnk/Desktop/Coding/tv-goldviewfx/backend/src/services/binance_full_backfill_service.ts)

Orchestrates full history fetch:
- Klines: walks backward from earliest DB row to exchange genesis, forward to now
- Agg trades: paginate by `fromId`, walking full history
- Funding rates: paginate by `startTime` (limit 1000)
- Mark/index/premium klines: same strategy as klines
- Sentiment data (OI stats, L/S, taker, basis): backfill rolling 30 days at all periods
- Rate limit aware with adaptive sleep

---

### 4. Nomad Jobs

#### [NEW] [gvfx-binance-worker.nomad.hcl](file:///Users/itsnk/Desktop/Coding/tv-goldviewfx/deploy/nomad/gvfx-binance-worker.nomad.hcl)

Service-type job. Tailscale sidecar + egress guard. Main task: `bun run src/jobs/binance_worker.ts`.
- WS connections for spot + futures live streaming
- REST polling for non-WS data (sentiment endpoints) every 5 min
- Uses `TIMESCALE_URL` from existing secrets, plus `BINANCE_API_KEY`/`BINANCE_SECRET_KEY`
- Constraints: linux, standby role, egress_worker=true
- Resources: cpu=1200, memory=2048

#### [NEW] [gvfx-binance-backfill.nomad.hcl](file:///Users/itsnk/Desktop/Coding/tv-goldviewfx/deploy/nomad/gvfx-binance-backfill.nomad.hcl)

Periodic batch job. Cron `*/5 * * * *`, `prohibit_overlap=true`. Runs `bun run scripts/binance-full-backfill.ts`. Same Tailscale pattern. Resources: cpu=1200, memory=2048.

