## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
- `backend/tests/unit/binance_client.test.ts` — HMAC signature, rate limit tracking, retry logic
- `backend/tests/unit/binance_market_data_ws.test.ts` — WS message parsing for all stream types
- `backend/tests/unit/binance_market_catalog.test.ts` — symbol normalization, pair parsing
- `backend/tests/integration/binance_market_data.test.ts` — end-to-end ingest with mock fetch

### Manual Verification
1. Schema: `psql` → verify all 13 `binance_*` tables + hypertables
2. Smoke: run backfill with `MAX_BATCHES=5` for BTCUSDT, verify DB rows
3. WS: start worker, verify live data after 1 min
4. Rate limits: monitor `X-MBX-USED-WEIGHT-1M` during backfill
